When Creating a list, the text of the second and following lines of a list item are not indented to the same level as the text in the first line.\\
Actually they are indented to the same level as the bullet in the first line.

i.E. they are formatted this way:\\
{{{

* list item\\
with some text\\
}}}

instead of\\
{{{

* list item\\
with some text\\
}}}
